## Getting Help

If you're experiencing issues with the Stein & Stevens app or have questions about its features, please don't hesitate to reach out. I'm here to help!

### How to Contact Support

- **Email:** benjaminharringtonrose@gmail.com
- **Response Time:** I typically respond within 24-48 hours
- **Best Time to Contact:** Monday-Friday, 9 AM - 5 PM EST

### When Contacting Support

To help me assist you more effectively, please include:

1. **Device Information:**

   - Device model (e.g., iPhone 15, Samsung Galaxy S24)
   - Operating system version
   - App version (found in Settings)

2. **Issue Description:**

   - What you were trying to do when the issue occurred
   - Steps to reproduce the problem
   - Any error messages you received
   - Screenshots (if applicable)

3. **Account Information:**
   - Your company/organization name
   - User role (Admin, Manager, Employee)

## App Features

Stein & Stevens is a comprehensive business management app designed for construction and contracting companies. Key features include:

### Time Tracking

- Clock in/out functionality
- Project-based time tracking
- Time entry management
- Overtime calculations

### Employee Management

- Employee profiles and information
- Role-based access control
- Team organization

### Project Management

- Project creation and tracking
- Project status monitoring
- Resource allocation

### Invoicing

- Invoice generation
- Client management
- Payment tracking
- Financial reporting

### Settings & Configuration

- User preferences
- App customization
- Data management

## Common Issues & Solutions

### Login Problems

- Ensure you have a stable internet connection
- Verify your email and password are correct
- Try logging out and logging back in
- Contact your administrator if you can't access your account

### Time Tracking Issues

- Make sure location services are enabled for accurate time tracking
- Check that you're connected to the internet when clocking in/out
- Verify your project assignments with your manager

### Data Sync Problems

- Ensure you have a stable internet connection
- Try closing and reopening the app
- Check if there are any pending updates

### App Performance

- Close other apps to free up memory
- Restart your device if the app is running slowly
- Ensure you have the latest app version installed

## Privacy & Security

Your data security and privacy are important to us. The app uses industry-standard encryption and follows best practices for data protection. All data is stored securely and is only accessible to authorized users within your organization.

